I saw this map a few time ago and thought that I have to play it on the Invasion server of my Clan.

My Clan-Leader asked the Author if I can convert the map and he said that we are allowed to do so.

Because of that I don't want to hear something like "You stole this map, you are a fu****g retard"

To those who don't understand this: Get a life, learn to read and look for friends that you can go on their nerves. Please let mine out of your boring life.

To everyone:
Please be fair when you play this map and report every Bug you find directly to me. You can send me a PN everytime or leave a message here.

If you gonna make this map on your Server please be so kind to inform me and send me the ip of it. may I will come and we can play together.


At least I have one question to everyone:
Can someone please create a .nav File for this map because my PC is way to bad for this big Map. If someone would do this please send me the file and I will add it.
